Description:
You arrive at the Happy Owl inn and notice Charls's dour presence immediately; he has an ale in one hand and a pie in the other but still manages to look unhappy.

Despite the lit fireplace, his frosty glare makes the entire tavern feel cold.
DescriptionAction: Did you bring enough gold to fund his retirement?
